-for running project 
    install packages using command
    npm i
-then make chnages in .env file
    add mongo database connection string
    and sendgrid api key for sending emails for forgot password
-to run code
    use any of the following command
    -node index.js
    -nodemon index.js
    -npm run dev
    -npm run start


